longBusinessSummary: VISA Steel Limited engages in the manufacture and sale of ferro alloys in India. It offers high carbon ferro chrome. The company was formerly known as Visa Industries Limited and changed its name to VISA Steel Limited in May 2005. VISA Steel Limited was incorporated in 1996 and is based in Bhubaneswar, India.
